title: Labor force participation rate, female (% of female population ages 15+) (modeled ILO estimate)
name: sl.tlf.cact.fe.zs
readme: The labor force participation rate is the labor force as a percent of the population ages 15 and older. The labor force is the sum of all persons of working age who are employed and those who are unemployed.
